---
import { LinkButton } from '@astrojs/starlight/components';
---

<section class="about not-content">
    <h2>What is yawa?</h2>

    <p><code>yawa</code> is yet another self-hosted web analytics platform but with no UI. Instead of dashboards, you query your data through the MCP, asking Claude or any compatible AI client questions about your traffic in plain language.</p>

    <ul>
        <li>
            <svg aria-hidden="true" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span><strong>Self-hostable</strong> - runs on a VPS or anywhere</span>
        </li>
        <li>
            <svg aria-hidden="true" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span><strong>Privacy-friendly</strong> - no cookie banners, no GDPR consent</span>
        </li>
        <li>
            <svg aria-hidden="true" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span><strong>LLM ready</strong> - ask Claude or any MCP client about your traffic</span>
        </li>
        <li>
            <svg aria-hidden="true" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span><strong>Full-featured</strong> - page views, referrers, events, web vitals and more</span>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <LinkButton href="/getting-started" variant="minimal" icon="right-arrow">Read docs</LinkButton>
</section>

<style>
    .about {
        padding-block: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    }

    .about h2 {
        color: var(--sl-color-white);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .about > p {
        font-size: var(--sl-text-body);
        color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        max-width: 60ch;
    }

    .about ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0 0 2rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.875rem;
    }

    .about li {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 10px;
        font-size: var(--sl-text-body);
        color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    }

    .about li svg {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        margin-top: 3px;
        color: var(--sl-color-accent);
    }

    .about li strong {
        color: var(--sl-color-white);
    }

    code {
        background-color: var(--sl-color-bg-inline-code);
        margin-block: -0.125rem;
        padding: 0.125rem 0.375rem;
        font-size: 0.875em;
    }
</style>